Package com.teracloud.streams.topology

Interface TSink

All Superinterfaces:
Placeable<TSink>, TopologyElement
public interface TSink extends TopologyElement, Placeable<TSink>
A handle to the sink of a TStream.

TSink implements Placeable to allow placement directives against its sink() processing. Calling a Placeable method on this will apply to the container that is executing the Consumer passed into sink().
